LEVEL 33
Monster Rancher Metropolis: Monster Rancher Card & Adventure Video Games: Monster Rancher Explorer Archive (Game Boy Color): Strategy: LEVEL 33
By Y.K. TAN on Saturday, May 29, 2004 - 11:38 pm:

Stage 33

Firstly, the naga + the jokers are irritatingly enough, so destroy all the boxes both on your right and on your left as well, so that the nagas can't reach you as you stand on tha metal block alone. When the jokers are out of range, quickly make a box staircase and head up and claim the key, than jump down to the metal block again. Destroy the box where the naga is going to the land(either on right or left, your choice, but I'm more situated on the right...). So time it perfectly that when the naga lands and crawls towards you, you jump over him (make sure that he's gonna die, or not you'll die) and make a box and climb out. As I said, that joker's will be irritating(true enough!) so make a box, just when the naga land, jump on the box, and create more boxes upwards and jump upwards. If this stills does not work, create more boxes to delay the movement of the joker than try to get all the way to the top.
